            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
              <td style="padding:0.8rem"><strong style="color:var(--gold)">緩起訴處分</strong></td>
              <td style="padding:0.8rem">繳一筆處分金到公庫，觀察期內不再犯就結案</td>
              <td style="padding:0.8rem;text-align:center">$20,000–$50,000</td>
              <td style="padding:0.8rem;text-align:center">❌ 無</td>
              <td style="padding:0.8rem;text-align:center">❌ 不影響</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
